{"tid":887591,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我係咪開始要將你睇得冇咁重要？","createTime":"2018-11-03T04:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T10:24:29.000Z","uid":16256,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1708ff3f3deb0917f0d2338e3552d199abd95c82","tid":887591,"uid":16256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T04:55:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的 幾日都冇咩同男朋友溝通同見面<br />\n<br />\n前日 我話想接佢收工 本來佢係電話到就話攰 <br />\n要番屋企 如果唔係我轉變語氣 佢先話同我食飯<br />\n如果唔係應該成個星期都見佢唔到<br />\n個晚佢番到去其實都係打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到左琴晚11點半 我終於同佢傾到電話<br />\n點知講唔夠兩句 佢就叫我訓教<br />\n然後又話佢可能都訓或者如果有朋友叫佢打機<br />\n佢就起床繼續打機 之後傾多兩句癈話佢就訓左 <br />\n最後我同佢咩都冇講到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身大家都好有默契咁會俾小小時間做自己野<br />\n佢有佢打機 我有我跑步 之後就會傾下計<br />\n但近排就好似同理想偏離得愈黎愈遠<br />\n呢幾日我都唔知點 番黎沖完涼就等佢電話 <br />\n搵佢又會話煩住佢 大前晚仲等到我訓著左<br />\n佢打過黎嘈醒左我 佢又叫番我訓教 自己又去左打機<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc30259a0e4b40b62fe6b8c60dde1c2132ca5cf1","tid":887591,"uid":177089,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T04:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/03/125817_42de6a11bafa83078147e56915af0bdb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F03%2F125817_42de6a11bafa83078147e56915af0bdb.png&h=e0d77c38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你情敵"},{"pid":"d71d7e16bc2ce178db824022e0242a79a85295db","tid":887591,"uid":16256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc30259a0e4b40b62fe6b8c60dde1c2132ca5cf1","tid":887591,"uid":177089,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T04:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/03/125817_42de6a11bafa83078147e56915af0bdb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F03%2F125817_42de6a11bafa8307814